modName: Unrelenting Force - Fus Ro Dah Ultra Power Mod
summary: Makes Unrelenting Force (Fus Ro Dah) much more powerful, and will send enemies flying.
descriptionHtml:
This simple modification for Skyrim makes Unrelenting force 6.67 times more powerful and will guaranteed, send enemies flying off into the distance.

INSTALL

Extract into steamapps/common/skyrim/data and activate via a mod manager or the launcher. Remove file to uninstall
author: Adonnus
